title: Which K-pop idols smile the least? - Quora

response.answer_text: BTS’ Suga. At first I didn’t added him because I’ve seen his smile so many times. And even if you search photos of him in Google his smile will pop up (and for some idols in this list you have to write specifically ‘smiling’). But a lot of people was requesting him so I decided to add him. He is serious but he is really funny too.  Twice’s Mina. She is the one who smiles the least in the group, she only does it in photoshoots or when something makes her very funny. She simply smirk... Her smile shows that she doesn't really smile that much. Anyway, she’s a beautiful woman.  Smirk.  Fake smile.  f(x)’s Krystal. I am not a fan, but I have NEVER seen this woman smile.  Smirk  Should smile often. She’s really pretty. Monsta X’s IM. I love this man. He is often serious, but he can also be weird and extra. Not the type that usually smiles.   BLACKPINK’s Jennie. She is kinda serious in photoshoots.  EXO’s Sehun. He looks serious but he isn’t.   Kris Wu. He's no longer an idol but I don't remember seeing his smile.  VIXX’s Leo. He doesn’t smile that often too.  MAMAMOO’s Hwasa. Ok, her image is more kind of sexy and she smiles, but I want to see it every time because her smile add years to my lifespan.  Ex-SISTAR’s Soyou. I never seen her smiling? Just smirks.  Couldn’t find a good photo. ): GFriend’s Umji.  A smile without teeth.  EXO’s Lay. This man is really REALLY handsome but never seen his smile? I don’t remember it.   NU’EST’s Ren. I find this man so cute and so beautiful but he is shy and doesn’t smile a lot.  A little but cute smile. SEVENTEEN’s Woozi: He looks kinda angry sometimes tbh  Red Velvet’s Irene: As Reveluv I saw my girl smile a lot of times but people still thinking she’s rude and cold (yes, she is cold but she’s a sweetheart) and I just love her smile.  UNIQ’s Wang Yibo. This man is really handsome, saw his smile twice but not many people has.  PENTAGON’s Wooseok. He is so handsome.  Busters’ Yeseo No smile (Why does she look so intimidating-)  Smile with no teeth  This is the only photo I could find of her smiling with her cute little bunny teeth. Look at how beautiful she is! CL. As a Blackjack, I could say she smiles a lot but some people haven’t see her smile. And she can eye-smile too.  IZ*ONE’s Hyewon.  That’s a smirk but it was the best photo I could find.  Here all of them were smiling but she wasn’t. :( CLC’s Seungyeon and Yeeun. They’re the type of person who smiles if the situation worths it.  Yeeun   (G)-IDLE’s Shuhua. She usually smile with no teeth.  *THIS POST IS ALWAYS OPEN TO UPDATE!

I know INFINITE's L (Kim Myungsoo) was told not to smile or laugh a lot, early in his career, because they wanted to portray a cold and aloof aura about him. He should definitely smile more though and express his emotions freely on screen. He's a visual so it's only natural that he'll look beautiful and handsome even/especially when smiling.    This is him with his cat named Byeol. He always talks about how much he loves his cat and other animals, so it's natural that being with his lovely pet makes him happy which, of course, causes him to smile.  I found this photo of him looking bright and happy. It's an old photo, but he looks really joyful and youthful here (well, he was younger). I hope more people listen to INFINITE. They've been around since 2010 and deserve more love and recognition for their talents.
